stix:STIX_Header.stix:Title: EUCOM JCC SR 037 16
stix:STIX_Header.stix:Description: EUCOM JCC identified new domains that may be linked to GREY CLOUD1 or GREY PRO2. The EUCOM JCC recommends alerting on any activity to the identified Indicators of Compromise (IOCs).
